Depends: ${misc:Depends}, python3, python3-dbus, python3-gi, python3-pyqt6 | python3-pyqt5, xclip | wl-copy, python3-markdown
Description: KRunner plugin for Mistral AI Vibe
 Katten is a KDE Plasma 6 KRunner plugin that allows you to send prompts
 to Mistral AI's Vibe service directly from KRunner (Alt+Space).
 .
 Features:
  * Send prompts to Mistral AI with web search capability
  * Preview panel with full markdown rendering (tables, code blocks, etc.)
  * Support for custom Mistral agents
  * Conversation history logged to XML
  * Multiple trigger keywords: katten, lechat, lc, mistral, vibe, mv
  * Fallback to simple API when web search fails
  * Warning message when fallback is used
 .
 This plugin is unofficial and not affiliated with Mistral AI.
